<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<p>Hello {{OWNER_NAME}},</p>

<p>This is an automated notification regarding the payment terms for Opportunity: <strong>{{OPPORTUNITY_NAME}}</strong>.</p>

<p>The status of the approval process has changed. Please review the details below:</p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" style="border: 1px solid #dddddd; margin: 20px 0;" width="100%">
	
		<tr style="background-color: #f3f3f3;">
			<td width="30%"><strong>Current Status:</strong></td>
			<td>{{CURRENT_STATUS}}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td><strong>Manager Remarks:</strong></td>
			<td>{{MANAGER_REMARKS}}</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td><strong>Client Remarks:</strong></td>
			<td>{{CLIENT_REMARKS}}</td>
		</tr>
	
</table>

<p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>If the status is <strong>Requested Changes</strong>, please log in to Salesforce, edit the payment terms according to the remarks, and resubmit.</li>
	<li>If the status is <strong>Client Approved</strong>, no further action is required on the terms. You may proceed with the project execution.</li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>